12 June 2017 Members of the media who applied for accreditation to cover the National Youth Day Commemoration taking place on 16 June 2017 at the Sport Grounds, Tshing ext. 2, Ventersdorp in North West are advised to collect their accreditation cards as follows:Date: 13 15 June 2017 Time: 09:00 17:00 Venue: Ventersdorp Local Municipality, Municipal Chamber, No 1 Van Tonder Crescent, Ventersdorp, North West ProvinceNB: You are required to bring your ID Book and Press Card or letter from the editor when collecting accreditation card.Media accreditation enquiries: Madimetja Moleba Cell: 072 842 6594 E-mail: madimetjam@dac.gov.zaFor more information/enquiries:Peter Mbelengwa Cell: 082 611 8197 E-mail: Peterm@dac.gov.zaPheliswa Sebati, 082 413 4609/ Pheliswa@gcis.gov.za Issued by Government Communication and Information System